## Pipeline

1. **`/spec`** ‚Äî `*.bundle.yaml` design v1 + testcase round 1. No `gen` / `codegen`.
2. **`/bqa-grill-docs`** ‚Äî UI, acceptance, breadcrumb, delete rules.
3. **`/dev-grill-docs`** ‚Äî codegen-ready bundle + `tags`; emit FE Codegenkit dry-run handoff.
4. **`/grill-with-docs`** ‚Äî optional reconcile when BQA‚ÜîDev contradict.
5. **`/update-spec`** / **`/update-spec-legacy`** ‚Äî controlled delta + `#update:*` (not full rewrite).
6. **`/prototype`** ‚Äî FE-lane handoff only after Codegenkit dry-run passes.

- Render: `docs_render` / `docskit render` (pnpm fallback during transition)
